disclaimer: work in progress

description:
============
a scalable feature-rich word alignment tool

dependencies:
=============
* boost 1.54
* libLBFGS
* MPI
* openfst-1.3.2
* python 2.7

how to build (with compiler: gcc 4.6.3 or clang 3.1-8):
==================================================
* make -f Makefile-latentCrfAligner

example invocation:
===================
```mpirun 32 latentCrfAligner [options]```

for an up-to-date list of options, ```latentCrfAligner --help```
